      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解起点是交易队列，然后进入Still状态。那Still之后有哪些分支？是直接进入风控检测吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Still可以触发FinTech_FraudDetection进行欺诈检测。同时Still也可以流转到Moving状态，表示交易开始处理。这两个分支是并行的业务路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，Still分出两条线，一条到风控检测，一条到Moving。那Moving状态有什么特点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Moving代表交易正在执行中，它可以回退到Still状态，比如处理超时后重置；也可能进入Crash状态，这是异常终止的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以Moving有两条出边，一条回到Still，一条到Crash。那Crash之后呢？系统如何恢复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Crash发生后，必须接入FinTech_AuthVault进行身份重认证，这是安全审计的强制要求，认证通过后才能重新入队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，整个流转闭环清楚了：队列→静止→风控/执行→可能崩溃→重认证。我确认一下结构：TransactionQueue启动Still，Still分叉到FraudDetection和Moving，Moving可回退或崩溃，Crash必须走AuthVault。可以开始绘制了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
